### An attempt was made
Here I am, trying to make these simulations more interactive. I accomplished my goal but I won't claim it's sophisticated or user-friendly. I imagine a web developer would be mortified. I hope to make this better over time, but my web development skills are... improving?

If you want to know how Giri's odd's change if he loses in round 5, you can! What if Shakh beats MVL in round 6? Have a peak.

Get started below by pressing some buttons. Wait until the page is done loading, or it might not work.
